---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Akademik - SMKN 14 Jakarta">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4" data-aos="fade-down">Program Akademik</h1>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          Program akademik yang komprehensif dan inovatif untuk mempersiapkan siswa menghadapi tantangan dunia kerja di era industri 4.0.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
        <div data-aos="fade-right">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Kurikulum Berbasis Industri</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Kurikulum kami dirancang berdasarkan kebutuhan industri terkini dengan mengintegrasikan teknologi terbaru dan soft skills yang dibutuhkan di dunia kerja.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Kurikulum berbasis kompetensi industri
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Pembelajaran berbasis proyek (Project Based Learning)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Sertifikasi kompetensi nasional dan internasional
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Kerjasama dengan industri terkemuka
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div data-aos="fade-left">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400/1D4ED8/FFFFFF?text=Program+Akademik"
               alt="Program Akademik SMKN 14 Jakarta"
               class="rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Teknik Komputer</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">Spesialisasi networking, hardware, dan software development</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-secondary-dark" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Multimedia</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">Desain grafis, animasi, dan produksi konten digital</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Elektronika</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">Sistem kontrol, elektronika, dan IoT</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-dark rounded-xl p-8 text-white text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Siap untuk Masa Depan?</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Bergabunglah dengan program akademik terbaik dan raih kesuksesan di dunia kerja.
        </p>
        <a href="/penerimaan" class="bg-secondary hover:bg-secondary-dark text-gray-900 font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition-all transform hover:scale-105 duration-300 shadow-lg">
          Daftar Sekarang
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>